---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">About Me</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2 text-sm">저를 소개합니다</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <!-- Avatar card -->
      <div class="fade-in flex justify-center" data-delay="100">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-56 h-56 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-green-400 p-1">
            <div class="w-full h-full rounded-3xl bg-[#1a1730] flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-7xl">👨‍💻</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-[#1e1b38] border border-amber-500/40 rounded-2xl px-4 py-2 text-center shadow-lg">
            <p class="text-amber-400 text-xs font-semibold">열정적인</p>
            <p class="text-white text-sm font-bold">개발자</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="fade-in space-y-5" data-delay="200">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
          코드로 세상을 만들어가는<br />
          <span class="gradient-text">이코딩</span>입니다
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          웹 개발에 열정을 가진 개발자로, 사용자 경험을 중시하며
          깔끔하고 효율적인 코드를 지향합니다.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          새로운 기술을 배우는 것을 즐기고, 창의적인 아이디어를
          현실로 구현하는 것에 보람을 느낍니다.
        </p>
        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-2">
          <div class="text-center p-3 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text">3+</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Years Exp.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-3 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text">20+</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Projects</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-3 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text">∞</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">열정</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
